Build-Type:     Simple
Author:         Boris Sukholitko <boriss@gmail.com>
Copyright:      Boris Sukholitko <boriss@gmail.com>
Maintainer:     Boris Sukholitko <boriss@gmail.com>
homepage:       https://github.com/bosu/pure-cdb
